Uses of Package
org.openwms.core.search

  • Packages that use org.openwms.core.search 
    Package Description
    org.openwms.core.search
    Definition and implementations of the action search feature.
  • Classes in org.openwms.core.search used by org.openwms.core.search 
    Class and Description
    Action
    An Action represents a possible UI action an User can take.
    Action.Builder
    A Builder class for Actions.
    Actions
    Encapsulates a collection of Actions and is mapped to the XML type "actions" in the ui-actions-schema.xsd.
    ActionService
    An ActionService is used to query Actions of a particular User or the whole application.
    Tag
    A Tag represents a search keyword in the OpenWMS.org ActionSearch concept.
    Tags
    Encapsulates a collection of Tags and is mapped to the XML type "tags" in the ui-actions-schema.xsd.
    VerbTag
    A VerbalTag represents a verb.
    VerbTag.Builder
    A Builder class for VerbTags.
